                 }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Appeal Court,makes no mention of any interlocutory or interim decision which may be   }
\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120\sl480\slmult0\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0{\rtlch \ltrch
                 }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
taken on appeal. Thus there is no express provision which recognises an appeal of an }
\par \pard\plain \s21\sb0\sa120\sl480\slmult0\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0{\rtlch \ltrch
                 }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
order granted by the Tribunal in terms of section 59. }
